{"tid":1203563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反送中】逸東酒店：追求平等、維護尊嚴　不反對員工明日添馬聚會 立場報道","createTime":"2019-06-11T12:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:00:03.000Z","uid":68738,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"92c64227956d009bea0e95a281b7319535274175","tid":1203563,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:53:46.000Z","msg":"政府強推《逃犯條例》修訂，全港多個界別發動罷工、罷市、罷課。佐敦逸東酒店今日表明，追求平等及維護尊嚴是其理念，將不反對員工明日於添馬公園聚會，「支持各員工以自己的方式發聲來愛護香港」。<br />\n<br />\n逸東酒店在FB發文，指酒店追隨「支持人類進步、追求平等及維護尊嚴」的理念，「為了尊重各位員工的政治立場，我們不反對員工們就逃犯條例修例參與6月12日於金鐘添馬公園的聚會，並支持各員工以自己的方式發聲來愛護香港。」<br />\n<br />\n逸東酒店稱，其服務或會受到有限度的影響，請各位見諒。"},{"pid":"0b0dfa098a12ab42c465565ff054c3ee5171416e","tid":1203563,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"下次去你度爆房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2405d1f8726e40e2c1a9decfab8708a4610dcf","tid":1203563,"uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0b0dfa098a12ab42c465565ff054c3ee5171416e","tid":1203563,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"下次去你度爆房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77517d96beb8b5bb3345510a34d46271323fd89","tid":1203563,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:00:03.000Z","msg":"聽日見逸東酒店既員工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/